# HopaHopa ŌĆō Project Overview

## Identity

- **App name:** HopaHopa ("Track your travels around the world with an interactive map")
- **Repo / workspace folder:** `TravelMap`
- **App ID (Capacitor):** `com.hopahopa.app`
- **iOS scheme:** `TravelMap`

## Stack

| Layer | Technology | Version |
|---|---|---|
| Framework | Angular (standalone, zoneless) | 20 |
| UI shell | Ionic | 8 |
| Native wrapper | Capacitor | 8 |
| Map | Mapbox GL JS | ~2.15 |
| Language | TypeScript | ~5.9 |
| Reactive | RxJS | ~7.8 |
| Tests | Karma + Jasmine | ŌĆö |
| Linter | Angular ESLint | ŌĆö |

**Zoneless change detection** is enabled via `provideZonelessChangeDetection()` in `src/app/app.config.ts`.  
**All components are standalone** ŌĆö never use `declarations: []` in modules.

## Build & output

- Build command: `ng build` ŌåÆ output directory **`www`** (`www/browser` for Capacitor `webDir`)
- Serve: `ng serve` / `npm start`
- Production env file (`environment.prod.ts`) replaces `environment.ts` via `angular.json` `fileReplacements`
- Test: `ng test` (Karma)
- Lint: `ng lint`

